{"tid":868554,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[發夢撚]有無巴打發啲好真實嘅夢","createTime":"2018-10-19T14:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T15:17:41.000Z","uid":860,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"49c39684bd55fb144740be8aaf8de51631e3c3ae","tid":868554,"uid":860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:38:58.000Z","msg":"當然，發夢嘅時候乜都覺得真<br />\n但最近發夢醒左會好清楚記得個夢<br />\n久而久之就開始唔知係發夢定真實<br />\n好似發夢個時同同事講左啲野，但原來根本現實無講過<br />\n但自己搞錯仲話：我之前咪講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家開始訓醒會寫低個夢啲事廢事又柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3fbc2734b9b7bfcbdab9ddda2f835e04db6bcb","tid":868554,"uid":145700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"有，但我個情況似係發春夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身十年都唔發一次夢，對上一次應該係親人死左先發夢見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但前幾日突然發夢自己係學校canteen見到好鍾意嘅偶像，仲要唔怕醜咁行過去問佢有冇人坐跟住坐係佢身邊，然後傾左好耐計好開心<br />\n醒左仲記得好清楚，但只係發生左一次<br />\n想再發多次夢見返佢都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}